Notable achievers in the field of forestry, forestry and wildlife conservation in the state of Maharashtra.
The decision to honour individuals with the "Maharashtra Van Bhushan" award is "Read here"
The Government has taken the Government Decision dated 05.02.2024. The decision was taken by the Maharashtra government.
Two committees, the Search and Scrutiny Committee and the Selection Committee, were constituted for the Vanbhushan Award.
